# chats_whitelist.txt — controls which chats the agent listens to
#
# Copy this file to chats_whitelist.txt and configure it.
# chats_whitelist.txt is gitignored and will never be committed.
#
# To find your chat IDs run:
#   python tools/list_chats.py
#
# Syntax:
#   *                     listen to ALL chats
#   *telegram*            only chats whose ID contains "telegram"
#   *signal*              only Signal chats
#   *telegram* *signal*   Telegram and Signal
#   !exactChatId          exclude this specific chat (takes priority over patterns)
#
# Examples:
#
# Listen to everything:
# *
#
# Only Telegram:
# *telegram*
#
# Everything except one group chat:
# *
# !someGroupChatId
#
# Specific chat IDs only:
# !abc123:beeper.local
# !xyz456:beeper.local
